ng\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9187da64386cf18e7646d9f997e6c9170d695785","tid":55192,"uid":21181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T08:23:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c778ee2acb4a8fe466858e4449b29ecae400971d","tid":55192,"uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T08:26:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有d倉頡撚好搞笑，以為人地打速成真係逐頁逐頁睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不過呢，我初學又係倉頡<br />\n<br />\n後來出現smartphone打字冇得靠記位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最慘係每個os d排位都唔同<br />\n<br />\n有得學都係學返倉頡好"},{"pid":"c7e5db60ece4637967a2d436c3b7850f2b3a3179","tid":55192,"uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T08:26:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有d倉頡撚好搞笑，以為人地打速成真係逐頁逐頁睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不過呢，我初學又係倉頡，之後用速成<br />\n<br />\n後來出現smartphone打字冇得靠記位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最慘係每個os d排位都唔同<br />\n<br />\n有得學都係學返倉頡好</blockquote>"},{"pid":"ac29d5f1c5eb0d976a5800a275535ddffab894a0","tid":55192,"uid":59047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T08:27:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>電腦速成，key背左快勁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n手機倉頡，去到一半有提示外加自動修正再加雙指極速輸入冇得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兩溝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人地手指廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打大鍵盤50%以上打錯key，又唔靈活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搞到仲慢過速成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"445a1669b90baf67154580b781a593ff6ae28285","tid":55192,"uid":39768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12